			<pubDate>Wed, 07 Oct 2015 08:58:18 GMT</pubDate>
			<description>‘Workers’ or slaves? Textbook maker backtracks after mother’s online complaint.  (http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/10/05/immigrant-workers-or-slaves-textbook-maker-backtracks-after-mothers-online-complaint/)</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/10/05/immigrant-workers-or-slaves-textbook-maker-backtracks-after-mothers-online-complaint/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">‘Workers’ or slaves? Textbook maker backtracks after mother’s online complaint. </a></div>

